{
  "stem": "5356.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And also we had shul, which was built in, you know-- it was 400 years old.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was a massive building with big, thick walls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "On the outside, it didn't look like much, but when you came inside-- the height of it with the center stage where the-- where you read the Torah, and [? what was ?] the steps to go up. 18 steps on each side to go up.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then the front where the [INAUDIBLE] was, where the chazan, you know, where the service is.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were steps where is choir, they was standing there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the floor was made out of tiles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was never heated because you're not allowed-- allowed to heat the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You're not allowed to heat it, so in wintertime, it was pretty cold.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we had a very famous [? rabbi ?] in the city.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "What-- the one of them, his great, great, great grandson was here in America, marching in the-- with him-- with Martin Luther King.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Yeshua Heschel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His great, great, great grandfather's name was Rabbi [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Scheuer ?] Heschel [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Memezebesch, ?] which, in Hebrew, the called him [SPEAKING HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was famous at home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the next rabbi, after this one, we had Rabbi [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Meier. ?] He was called, [SPEAKING HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in his-- in his [INAUDIBLE] site, the day when he died, it was remembered.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "People from all over Poland came to the city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Wrote little notes, you know, and put it down on his-- on his-- where he was-- he had a special house built for him, you know, for-- where he was buried.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's where people put those-- all those requisitions--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember when he died because he died, you know, in the 1700s.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
